      <p>In this study, we have used standard parameters for the evaluation of prediction models. Here, we have calculated both threshold dependent as well as independent parameters. In the case of threshold-dependent parameters we have computed, sensitivity (Sens), specificity (Spec), accuracy (Acc) and Matthews correlation coefficient (MCC) using the following equations (1-4). In addition, we have measured the performance of models with a well-established and threshold-independent parameter Area Under the Receiver Operating Characteristic (AUROC) curve.</p>
