    <sec id="s3_6">
      <label>3.6</label>
      <title>Machine learning based prediction</title>
      <p>Various machine learning classifiers such as RF, DT, GNB, XGB, KNN, ETN, SVCN and LR are used to develop a prediction model. For this, we have computed the features of disease causing and disease non-causing peptides using composition-based module of Pfeature.</p>
